ine luminosity in phase, if the truncation radius is small enough for\nDoppler effects due to disk orbital motion to significantly affect the observed\nradiation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2020 02:51:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2020 16:57:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-21"}
