 in the density-of-states, which signals the emergence\nof a correlated-state. The described approach of 2D crystal buckling offers a\nstrategy for creating other superlattice systems and, in particular, for\nexploring interaction phenomena characteristic of flat-bands.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2020 03:26:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-15"}
